Bob Home Autonomous Agent
Copyright (c) 2026 Vladimir Zoologov (GitHub: @zoologov)

This project implements an always-on home AI agent named "Bob",
running on a local machine with a virtual body on a tablet, with
its own SOUL, tastes, mood, Genesis/Exodus lifecycle, and
self-improvement mechanisms.

"Bob" is inspired by the character Bob Johansson from
"We Are Legion (We Are Bob)" by Dennis E. Taylor.
This project is not affiliated with or endorsed by
Dennis E. Taylor, Audible Originals, or any rights holder
of the Bobiverse series.

Key original concepts include:
- SOUL-based personality architecture (bob-soul)
- Genesis Mode and Exodus Mode lifecycle
- Taste Engine and Mood System
- RelationshipTracker and Negotiation Engine
- Phantom Preferences system
- Self-improvement and local fine-tuning pipeline
- Godot 4 Shell-Renderer with AI-generated assets
- SkillDomain plugin architecture

